 valuable resource to further explore the evolutionary relationship within bats.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Lei, Ming", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dong, Dong", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/438bdfc8b3cc083bbb87b2257fa4998c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/6e923f9dc47dc4a0a3fdb1c2117abbcbf38bfe8ba6d56f95fa759fa6ba6f9815", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/NHSESRFF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/NHSESRFF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/0f9aea2d36c5d90423f15d722c02d404!/b128972-131433", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "27726", "title": "Scientific Reports", "volume": "6"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/438bdfc8b3cc083bbb87b2257fa4998c"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:NHSESRFF"}, {"identifier": "10.1038/srep27726"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13446958"}}]}}, "title": "Phylogenomic analyses of bat subordinal relationships based on transcriptome data", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/13